# Documentation - Only these files are allowed:
# ✓ README.md (main overview with quick links)
# ✓ INSTALLATION.md (setup & deployment guide)
# ✓ FEATURES.md (feature list)
# ✓ API_DOCUMENTATION.md (API endpoints & examples)
# ✓ LICENSE.md (licensing information)
# ✓ PROJECT_COMPREHENSIVE_ANALYSIS.md (technical deep dive)
# All other .md and doc files below these will be ignored
